WEBVTT

00:00.801 --> 00:03.404
(THEME MUSIC PLAYING)

00:24.658 --> 00:28.162
We're here live
at the Metropolis
Christmas Eve Festival,

00:28.196 --> 00:31.465
where thousands
of kids are ready
to greet Santa Claus.

00:31.499 --> 00:34.635
With me now
is six-year-old Keely Miller.

00:34.668 --> 00:37.805
Keely, what do you hope
Santa brings you this year?

00:37.838 --> 00:39.573
Um, a teddy bear?

00:39.607 --> 00:41.575
Why don't you go ahead
and ask Santa now?

00:41.609 --> 00:43.344
Santa, Santa,
please bring me...

00:43.377 --> 00:44.612
-MAN: What's going on?
-(ALL CLAMORING)

00:44.645 --> 00:46.247
(GROWLING)

00:47.781 --> 00:49.183
(GRUNTS)

00:51.485 --> 00:54.188
This is gonna take a lot more
tranquilizer arrows.

00:54.222 --> 00:55.489
Slow him down.

00:55.523 --> 00:56.557
Yee-haw!

00:57.691 --> 00:59.727
Head along, little Grundy.

00:59.760 --> 01:01.162
(SCREAMING)

01:03.531 --> 01:05.266
(GROANING)

01:06.334 --> 01:08.702
Are you kidding me?

01:08.736 --> 01:09.737
(LAUGHING MANIACALLY)

01:09.770 --> 01:11.139
GREEN ARROW: Hey, ugly!

01:12.240 --> 01:13.374
(BOTH GRUNT)

01:15.209 --> 01:16.377
(SCREAMS)

01:20.781 --> 01:22.450
-(BOTH GASP)
-Oh.

01:25.319 --> 01:27.255
(STUTTERS) Teddy?

01:27.288 --> 01:30.391
Not Teddy. Grundy!

01:30.424 --> 01:32.526
-(GROWLS)
-(SCREAMS)

01:35.663 --> 01:36.664
(GRUNTS)

01:38.799 --> 01:40.234
(GROANS)

01:43.804 --> 01:45.473
Mommy.

01:45.506 --> 01:46.507
Finally.

01:48.542 --> 01:51.479
All right, Plas, you get
Grundy back to his cell
at S.T.A.R. Labs,

01:51.512 --> 01:52.813
then pick up some ice
on your way.

01:52.846 --> 01:55.649
(MUFFLED) On my way to...

01:56.784 --> 01:57.885
Where?

01:57.918 --> 02:00.588
Plas, my Christmas party.

02:01.855 --> 02:05.326
Right! Which is at...

02:05.359 --> 02:07.595
7:30. You better be there.

02:07.628 --> 02:09.463
You know how hard it was
for me to find a banquet hall

02:09.497 --> 02:10.864
that's insured
for meta-humans?

02:10.898 --> 02:12.700
Okay! Okay! Just ice?

02:12.733 --> 02:15.569
I can pick up
a few pizzas if you want.

02:15.603 --> 02:16.504
Pizzas?

02:16.537 --> 02:18.472
It's a Christmas party,
not a prison rodeo.

02:18.506 --> 02:20.574
You know what?
I'll get the ice.

02:20.608 --> 02:22.243
You won't get the right kind.

02:23.511 --> 02:25.213
Of ice?

02:26.780 --> 02:28.482
(MUSIC PLAYING)

02:38.659 --> 02:41.662
Gambo croquettes
with saffron aioli.

02:41.695 --> 02:43.464
You got any of those
little hot dogs

02:43.497 --> 02:44.765
wrapped in biscuit dough?

02:45.499 --> 02:46.500
(GROANS)

02:46.534 --> 02:48.636
I mean... Yeah, you know,
these look terrific.

02:53.541 --> 02:54.542
(BURPS)

02:58.446 --> 02:59.613
GREEN ARROW: Was that...

03:05.653 --> 03:07.621
No, no. I guess it wasn't.

03:10.758 --> 03:12.260
Oh, poor thing.

03:12.293 --> 03:14.362
I know. It's just so sad.

03:14.395 --> 03:16.664
He's gotta know
he's not coming.

03:16.697 --> 03:18.732
-Who's not coming?
-Batman.

03:18.766 --> 03:19.767
And who cares?

03:20.901 --> 03:22.670
Pumpkin carrot soup shooters.

03:23.837 --> 03:26.840
Wait! I almost forgot
the bat signal croutons.

03:26.874 --> 03:29.310
Come one, Green Arrow,
get with it!

03:29.777 --> 03:31.945
Oh... Why?

03:31.979 --> 03:35.349
GA has this whole imaginary
bromance thing with Batman.

03:35.383 --> 03:36.784
He wants to be friends
outside work

03:36.817 --> 03:39.387
and he thinks the Christmas
party is his way in.

03:39.420 --> 03:41.322
Yeah, not that Batman cares.

03:41.355 --> 03:43.824
He spends every Christmas
Grinching it up in his cave

03:43.857 --> 03:47.928
while GA toasts bat signal
croutons and saves him a seat.

03:49.597 --> 03:51.432
Well, this is just
about the easiest

03:51.465 --> 03:52.833
Christmas present
I can think of.

03:54.902 --> 03:55.903
Oh, no.

03:59.840 --> 04:01.575
Oh, hi, Batman.

04:01.609 --> 04:03.377
I didn't think
you were coming.

04:04.345 --> 04:06.914
Put. Me. Down.

04:10.484 --> 04:11.752
(GLASSES SHATTERING)

04:11.785 --> 04:12.786
(DRINK SPILLING)

04:14.922 --> 04:15.923
Hey!

04:18.459 --> 04:20.528
It's a Christmas miracle.

04:21.061 --> 04:24.365
Hmm. Socks, jelly beans.

04:24.398 --> 04:26.033
Whoo, really nice watch.

04:26.066 --> 04:28.001
More socks.

04:28.035 --> 04:31.539
Let's get this party started!

04:35.443 --> 04:37.044
All right, everybody.
In a few minutes,

04:37.077 --> 04:38.646
I'll be reading Twas the...

04:38.679 --> 04:40.714
What's that ghoul doing here?

04:40.748 --> 04:44.418
I know, right? I didn't think
Batman was comin' either.

04:45.719 --> 04:47.788
-It's drooling.
-(GROWLING)

04:47.821 --> 04:49.790
That's just because
of the tranquilizers.

04:49.823 --> 04:52.860
He's so out of it,
you won't even know he's here!

04:52.893 --> 04:53.894
(GRUMBLING)

04:56.530 --> 04:57.698
(GRUNDY GRUMBLING)

04:59.367 --> 05:01.569
Munchies.

05:02.403 --> 05:04.472
(GRUMBLING)

05:05.973 --> 05:08.376
There goes Zatanna's
figgy pudding.

05:08.409 --> 05:10.611
Oh, I tried it last year.

05:10.644 --> 05:12.079
Better him than us.

05:12.112 --> 05:14.014
You were supposed to take
that thing to S.T.A.R. Labs!

05:14.047 --> 05:16.550
I did! I tried. But...

05:16.584 --> 05:18.352
But what? What?

05:18.386 --> 05:20.788
(GRUNTS)
They were in the middle
of their Christmas party,

05:20.821 --> 05:22.623
and I didn't want to
make a scene,

05:22.656 --> 05:25.393
so I figured we could
keep him for a few hours.

05:25.426 --> 05:26.994
What?

05:27.027 --> 05:30.364
S.T.A.R. Labs
scheduled their party
the same night as mine?

05:30.398 --> 05:31.665
Oh, okay.
All right, all right.

05:31.699 --> 05:33.767
Oh, yeah, and it's amazing!

05:33.801 --> 05:36.036
Whoo, they have a peppermint
chocolate fountain

05:36.069 --> 05:37.738
and Santa's there.

05:37.771 --> 05:40.508
Though it might just be the
Professor Hamilton guy.

05:40.541 --> 05:41.975
Twinsies!

05:43.477 --> 05:44.712
Hey, big fella,
that's not cheese.

05:44.745 --> 05:46.880
Let's save some
for everyone, okay?

05:46.914 --> 05:47.915
(GRUNTS)

05:52.420 --> 05:56.557
Oh, I was looking forward
to Martian Manhunter's
banana cream pie.

05:56.590 --> 05:58.158
Listen to me,
you shape-shifting freak.

05:58.191 --> 06:00.428
If I didn't have three dozen
cinnamon pecan roundies

06:00.461 --> 06:02.630
coming out of that oven
in exactly 45 seconds, I...

06:02.663 --> 06:04.898
-(BELL DINGS)
-What?

06:04.932 --> 06:07.801
Don't worry, GA,
I'm totally in control of...

06:07.835 --> 06:10.170
That thing is a soulless
undead animal.

06:10.203 --> 06:11.705
Capable of who knows what.

06:11.739 --> 06:14.642
Keep it subdued or I will.

06:17.945 --> 06:21.749
Okay, Grunster, let's
sit you down right here.

06:21.782 --> 06:25.919
-(GRUMBLING)
-And look, Christmas cartoons!

06:27.521 --> 06:29.857
Hmm. Pretty.

06:30.591 --> 06:31.925
Sweet rich cocoa,

06:31.959 --> 06:34.662
just in time for the
Secret Santa gift exchange.

06:34.695 --> 06:38.899
Oh, yeah.
Mine's in... In the car.

06:38.932 --> 06:40.701
Hey, Zatanna, I'm
your Secret Santa

06:40.734 --> 06:42.503
and I got you
something really...

06:42.536 --> 06:44.538
Well, special.

06:44.572 --> 06:46.139
You're not
Zatanna's Secret Santa,

06:46.173 --> 06:47.575
I'm Zatanna's Secret Santa.

06:47.608 --> 06:49.677
Hey, Superman,
I'm your Secret Santa

06:49.710 --> 06:51.445
and I got you
something really...

06:51.479 --> 06:53.146
Well, special.

06:53.180 --> 06:55.716
Oh, uh... Mmm.

06:55.749 --> 06:59.820
Gas station
clearance bin at best.

06:59.853 --> 07:02.723
REPORTER: (ON TV)
Holiday havoc in
downtown Metropolis today,

07:02.756 --> 07:04.892
as the annual Christmas
parade was attacked

07:04.925 --> 07:06.494
by the savage Solomon Grundy.

07:06.527 --> 07:10.664
This young eye witness
encountered that
terrifying creature.

07:10.698 --> 07:14.001
(WHIMPERING) I... I was asking
Santa for a teddy bear

07:14.034 --> 07:16.036
when the big scary man
smashed him.

07:16.069 --> 07:17.838
(GROWLS)

07:17.871 --> 07:19.873
Fortunately,
Justice League heroes

07:19.907 --> 07:22.009
Green Arrow and Plastic Man
were on hand

07:22.042 --> 07:24.211
to stop the mindless monster.

07:24.244 --> 07:26.814
GRUNDY:
Grundy, remember,

07:26.847 --> 07:28.516
fight enemies.

07:28.549 --> 07:29.817
(GASPS)

07:29.850 --> 07:33.186
Now, Grundy, here.

07:33.220 --> 07:35.756
Grundy with enemies!

07:35.789 --> 07:38.592
Grundy, destroy them!

07:38.626 --> 07:41.729
Grundy destroy enemies!

07:41.762 --> 07:43.931
SUPERMAN:
Uh, excuse me,
um, Grundy,

07:43.964 --> 07:46.800
no one should be without
a present at Christmas.

07:46.834 --> 07:48.235
-For you.
-(GRUMBLES)

07:49.670 --> 07:50.838
Hmm.

07:59.112 --> 08:00.113
(CLEARS THROAT)

08:01.815 --> 08:03.216
Yeah, um...

08:03.250 --> 08:04.251
(RUMBLING)

08:04.985 --> 08:07.688
Holy Hannah, my tree!

08:07.721 --> 08:10.991
Oh, and... Yeah, Grundy
has escaped. Gone.

08:12.593 --> 08:13.794
Batman, you take the...

08:13.827 --> 08:16.029
Batman? Batman?

08:16.063 --> 08:17.130
(GROWLING)

08:19.299 --> 08:20.534
(GRUNTS)

08:26.106 --> 08:27.107
(GRUNTS)

08:28.141 --> 08:29.577
(GROANS)

08:29.610 --> 08:30.811
(GRUNTS)

08:38.619 --> 08:39.787
(GROANS)

08:49.997 --> 08:52.232
-Sled, now!
-(GRUNTS)

08:54.067 --> 08:54.968
Hey.

08:55.002 --> 08:56.904
That looks just like
the teddy I gave Grundy.

08:56.937 --> 08:58.205
No wonder he's mad.

08:58.238 --> 08:59.940
Why does everybody
hate that bear?

08:59.973 --> 09:02.676
Wait! I know
where Grundy is going.

09:02.710 --> 09:04.311
Everyone, follow Batman.

09:04.344 --> 09:06.614
Flash, I need to
find somebody. Fast.

09:06.647 --> 09:08.115
We're comin' out
by the street.

09:08.148 --> 09:10.751
Maybe we should
start slowing down.

09:10.784 --> 09:12.185
Sleds can't talk.

09:12.219 --> 09:13.086
(SCREAMING)

09:13.120 --> 09:14.554
PLASTIC MAN: Ho-ho-ho!

09:16.356 --> 09:17.791
(SCREAMING)

09:17.825 --> 09:19.092
(BOTH GRUNT)

09:26.700 --> 09:27.868
Leave him be!

09:29.236 --> 09:31.605
Are you insane?

09:31.639 --> 09:33.974
Trust me. Come on over.

09:36.243 --> 09:37.778
Aw!

09:37.811 --> 09:39.613
What's going on?

09:39.647 --> 09:41.114
Hey, there. It's okay.

09:42.816 --> 09:43.984
(GRUMBLING)

09:44.818 --> 09:49.256
Uh, Grundy sorry. Scare you.

09:53.727 --> 09:55.062
For you.

09:55.095 --> 09:59.266
No one be without present
at Christmas.

10:00.267 --> 10:01.268
Teddy.

10:06.707 --> 10:07.875
Mmm.

10:13.413 --> 10:16.083
Wow! Who needs
a big fancy party?

10:16.116 --> 10:17.651
I could stay here...

10:17.685 --> 10:18.852
Oh, my...

10:18.886 --> 10:21.021
You know,
the S.T.A.R. Labs party

10:21.054 --> 10:22.723
is like two blocks away.

10:22.756 --> 10:23.924
Race ya.

10:25.926 --> 10:27.895
Well, it is Christmas Eve.

10:27.928 --> 10:30.330
I still can't believe they
scheduled it the same night.

10:30.363 --> 10:31.131
I mean, the nerve.

10:31.164 --> 10:35.068
Okay, well,
maybe see you there.

10:41.809 --> 10:44.044
Be sure
to invite me next year.

10:45.913 --> 10:47.080
I did it.

10:47.881 --> 10:49.983
I really did it.

10:50.017 --> 10:52.085
Hey, guys,
what about my party?

10:52.119 --> 10:53.921
Uh, we've got the hall
till midnight.

10:53.954 --> 10:55.155
Uh, there's a disco ball!

11:02.429 --> 11:04.965
(THEME MUSIC PLAYING)
